{
  "chapter": 83,
  "chapter_summary": "第八十三回\"自作自受\"。花无缺在苏樱照料下停止大笑但仍受笑穴毒针所困，苏樱以替他逼出毒针为由，套出花无缺\"移花接玉\"内功要诀。白山君夫妇携江玉郎、铁萍姑在谷外等候，苏樱回来后声称已问出秘密但拒绝立即交出，白山君夫妇无可奈何。白山君派江玉郎去用美男计从苏樱口中套取秘密。江玉郎自以为老手，对不会武功的苏樱志在必得，谁知反被苏樱识破计谋。苏樱假意与他调情，喂他服下所谓\"百病百疼催生丸\"，将江玉郎整治得痛苦不堪，令其自食恶果。全章展现苏樱聪慧过人、手段高明，将花无缺与江玉郎两人都玩弄于股掌之间。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "那人",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "出去出去，我说过我不要吃这劳什子的草根树皮，你为何总是要给我吃？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming_lao_zhe",
      "text": "这不是草根树皮，这是人参。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "那人",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "管他是人参鬼参，我说不吃，就是不吃。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming_lao_zhe",
      "text": "也没见过你这样的人，好好好，你不吃，我就拿出去。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那人不吃，她难道就要拿来给我吃么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "多谢姑娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "现在你还不必谢我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "为……为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你现在笑声虽已停止，但那根针还是留在你气穴里，只不过被我用药力逼得偏了些，没有触入你的笑穴，但你只要一用力，旧疾还是难免复发。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "这……这又该如何是好？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "但……但我现在连一丝气力都使不出来。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你现在自然使不出来的，你若能使得出来，也就不必来找我了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "姑娘难道有什么法子，能令我真气贯通无碍？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "自然有的，此刻你只要将你所练内功的要诀告诉我，我便可在旁助你一臂之力，使你真气贯通，逼出毒针。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你难道是怕我偷学你的内功么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "在下并无此意，只不过……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "像我这洋的人，若是有一分爱武的心，此刻纵非天下第一高手，只怕也差不多了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你们这些练武的人，总将自己的武功视若珍宝，又怎知这件事在我眼中看来，简直不值一文。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "姑娘慢走。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "说不说虽由得你，但我听不听，还不一定哩。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "在下所练内功，名日“移花接玉”，乃是……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我实在想不出这位苏姑娘究竟是位怎么样的人？两位前辈竟对她如此倾倒。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "小伙子，我告诉你，你见了她时，只怕连话都说不出来了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "前辈未免也说得太玄了，难道在下竟如此……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "好妹子，你果然来了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "‘移花接玉’的秘密，妹子你想必也问出来了。",
      "tone": "期待",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "不错，我问出来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "多谢多谢……",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "你现在还不必急着来谢我。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "那么……那么……妹子你难道已将‘移花接玉’的窍诀写下来了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "是，是，妹子自然会写下来给我们的，老太婆你急什么？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "我现在也不准备写下来给你们。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "那么……那么妹子你的意思是……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "妹子你要到什么时候才肯告诉我们呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "也许三天五天，也许一年半载，也许十年八年，等我玩够了，我自然会告诉你们的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "好妹子，你别开玩笑，若是等十年八年，岂非急也把人急死了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "你们急不急死，是你们的事，与我又有何关系？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "但……但妹子你不是已答应了我……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "我只答应你，要叫花无缺说出‘移花接玉’的秘密，并末答应将这秘密告诉你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "深山无以待客，我也不留你们了，你们还是回去吧！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "妹子请留步。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "你们总该知道，我说出的话永无更改，何苦再多事。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我只想问问那姓花的现在怎么样了？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "你们只管放心，我也绝不会放了他他这辈子只怕是再也休想见人了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位姑娘好大的架子。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "这丫头既然手无缚鸡之力，前辈为何不拿下她来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "老头子拿她当宝贝一样，谁若碰着她一根手指，老头子不拼命才怪，我夫妇现在还不想惹那老头子，也只好放她一马了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "何况，你莫看她于无缚鸡之力，但鬼心眼却还足真多，我们这几个人，倒真还未必能制得住她",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你莫非不服气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "好小子，我早就听说你对女人另有一套，你去试试，那丫头正在有些春心荡漾，说不定真的会告诉你",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "在下对女人有何本事？前辈说笑了。",
      "tone": "谦虚",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "好妹子，你就让他去吧，嫂子我保证他不敢对你变心，他若敢变心，嫂子我就叫小白将他脑袋咬下来。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你是谁？凭什么冒冒失失地闯入这里来？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "在下冒昧闯入，实在无礼……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你既知无礼，此刻就该快些退出去。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "姑娘慢走，姑娘你好歹要救在下一命？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你若有病，就该去看医生，此间既未悬壶，也未开业，你来干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "别人若是医得了在下的病，在下又怎敢来麻烦姑娘？只叹世间的名医虽多，却都是欺世盗名之辈，他们若有姑娘的一成本事，在下……唉，在下也不必千里迢迢地赶来打扰姑娘了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你又怎知道我能治得了你的病？是谁告诉你的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "这……这是在下的一位父执前辈，不忍见在下无救而死，才指点在下一条明路，而且将在下带来这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "这位前辈不许在下说出他的名讳，但在下在姑娘面前，又怎敢说谎，指点在下前来的，就是白山君白老前辈和他的夫人。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 213
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "这两口子倒真是会替我找麻烦。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "在下这病，别人反正也救不了的，姑娘今日若不肯……不肯可怜可怜我，我就索性死在姑娘面前吧！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你倒真是会缠人……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "姑娘走不得，姑娘好歹也得救在下一命。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "呆子，我走了，你难道不会跟我来么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "现在，你不妨先告诉我，你得的是什么病？是哪里觉得不舒服？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "在下……在下肚子疼得很厉害。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "但我瞧你却不像疼得很厉害的样子。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "在下在姑娘面前，怎敢放肆？何况，无论是谁，见到姑娘这样天仙般的人物，也会将疼痛浑然忘却了的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你看到我既然就能止疼，那还要医什么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "在下若能常伴姑娘左右，疼死也无妨，只不过……只不过……",
      "tone": "期待",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你瞧你，疼成这样子，还不快躺下来。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "多谢姑娘。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你若不乖乖的躺上床，我就不理你了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "是是，我听话就是。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "听话的才是乖孩子，姐姐买糖给你吃。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我疼……疼得更厉害了，你快来……快来瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你哪里疼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "这里……就在这里。",
      "tone": "期待",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你现在觉得好些了么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "好些了……但你不能停手，一停手我就疼。",
      "tone": "期待",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "别人都说这位苏姑娘是如何如何的厉害，但在我看来，也不过只是个初解风情的黄毛丫头而已．只要我略施妙计，还不是一样立刻手到擒来。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "这是我精心配成的清灵镇痛丸，不但可止疼，而且还大补，你现在吃下去，肚子立刻就不疼了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我不吃。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "为什么不吃？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我一吃，肚子就不疼了，我肚子若是不疼，姑娘岂非就不肯…不肯替我揉了。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "小坏蛋……好，你吃下去，我还是替你揉的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "这药苦不苦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "这药非但不苦，而且还甜得很，简直就像糖一样，来，乖乖的张开嘴，我喂你吃下去。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "那人",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "酒呢？没有酒了，苏樱小丫头，快拿酒来。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你乖乖的躺在这里，我去去就来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你若站起来乱跑，我可就不理你了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_lao_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "那人",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "姓苏的丫头，你耳朵聋了么？怎地还不来。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_wu_ming_lao_zhe",
      "text": "来了来了，我这就替你拿酒去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "白山君呀白山君，你以为我听到这秘密后，会告诉你么？你若真的以为我会告诉你，你可就是天下第一个大笨蛋了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你说谁是天下第一个大笨蛋？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "谁若敢说姑娘是丫头，谁就是天下第一个大笨蛋。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "那不过是个老糊涂，老酒鬼，咱们犯不上理他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "是是是，咱们不理他。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 333,
      "line_end": 333
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你笑得这么开心，肚子不疼了么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 335,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "疼……疼得更历害了，求姑娘再替我揉揉。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "其实，你心里本认为我才是天下第一个大傻蛋，是么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我怎敢这么想，我难道晕了头了！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 347,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你认为我很年轻，又没见过什么男人，一定很容易上男人的当，你觉得你对女人很有一手，略施妙计，就可以令我投怀送抱，而且将那‘移花接玉’的秘密，老老实实地告诉你……是么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 349,
      "line_end": 349
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "哪……哪有这样的事，姑娘你……你太……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "何况，你知道我丝毫不会武功，就算看透了你的心意，也没法子拿你怎样，所以你的胆子就更大了，是么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "姑娘千万莫要错怪了好人，在下绝无此意。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你不但有这意思，而且到了必要时，还想来个‘霸王硬上弓’，反正我也无力抗拒．那时生米煮成熟饭，我还能不乖乖的听话么？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "姑娘不能冤枉我，我若有此意，就叫我不得好死。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "到了这时，你还想你能好死么？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我……我……姑娘……哎哟！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你要我替你揉肚子，我就替你揉肚子，你可知我为何如此听话？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "在……在下不知道，求姑娘莫要揉了吧！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 377,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "现在你觉得疼了，就要我莫要揉了么？但我知道你的肚子很疼，病很重，怎能忍心不替你揉？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 381,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我……我没有病……一点病也没有。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 385,
      "line_end": 385
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你没有病？为何要骗我？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 387,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我有病，有病……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 389,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "对了，你不但有病，而且病很重，而且越来越重，到后来纵然是一片纸落在你手上，你也会觉得有如刀割。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 393,
      "line_end": 393
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "求……求姑娘救救我，救救我……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 395
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "现在我也没法子救你了，只因我方才拿错了药，拿给你吃的，不是清灵镇痛丸，而是百病百疼催生丸。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 83,
      "line_start": 401,
      "line_end": 401
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "百病百疼催生丸？这是什么药？",
